"data/events_mantis.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"MANTIS_GAMBLE\"]/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "你不跟骗子玩。在超光速驱动器充电时与船员交谈。"

#: src-ru/data/events_mantis.xml.rawclobber:272
msgid ""
"data/events_mantis.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"MANTIS_GAMBLE_BLUE\"]/event[1]/text"
msgstr ""
"穿[style[color:5f97ff]]蓝色[[/style]]的那个被逼到了角落。就在最后一刻，他扑上去砍下了对手的头。你拿走了你的赢利！"

#: src-ru/data/events_mantis.xml.rawclobber:279
msgid ""
"data/events_mantis.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"MANTIS_GAMBLE_BLUE\"]/event[2]/text"
msgstr ""
"看起来穿[style[color:5f97ff]]蓝色[[/style]]的螳螂正在占上风，对对手连连猛击。突然，穿[style[color:ff4551]]红色[[/style]]的那位以一记精准的攻击结束了战斗。"

#: src-ru/data/events_mantis.xml.rawclobber:281
